      "writtenOn": "2026-06-10T21:08:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Since this log would never be useful on any systems that don\u0027t implement /run/boot-device, would it be OK to just skip its creation if it doesn\u0027t exist?",
      "revId": "eb49b51aec543932362b65ed44de2eb0702f6f82",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "965dc44d_c45e5a84",
        "filename": "bmc_state_manager.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 10
      },
      "lineNbr": 279,
      "author": {
        "id": 1002558
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-06-11T01:00:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hi @spinler@us.ibm.com,\nBased on this change (https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/openbmc/+/90871), it seems that `Unknown` should be the default value.\n\nOr does IBM never have this path at all? If the path is never present on IBM systems, I can add a condition to skip it.\n\nIf we decide to skip it, are there any additional conditions you would like to add? For example, should we log an info, or should we simply skip it if the path `/run/boot-device` cannot be found?",
      "parentUuid": "d345258e_4cce9828",
      "revId": "eb49b51aec543932362b65ed44de2eb0702f6f82",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "26d33619_1b6804a6",
        "filename": "bmc_state_manager.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 10
      },
      "lineNbr": 279,
      "author": {
        "id": 1000000
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-06-11T01:30:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "@spinler@us.ibm.com -\n\n1. Don\u0027t you want the RebootCause even if you don\u0027t have a way to identify the boot device?\n\n2. I implemented this for the static-norootfs layout but it should be pretty straight-forward for someone to add this file to the init scripts of other flash layouts.  I assume you have some level of redundancy in your boot device?",
      "parentUuid": "965dc44d_c45e5a84",
      "revId": "eb49b51aec543932362b65ed44de2eb0702f6f82",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": false,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "fae63fb9_9303d663",
        "filename": "bmc_state_manager.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 10
      },
      "lineNbr": 279,
